### 2) Structured Data Suggestions

- Use [JSON-LD](https://developers.google.com/search/docs/advanced/structured-data/intro-structured-data) format for structured data.
- Implement structured data for product schema, including attributes such as `name`, `description`, offer details (like `price`, `availability`), and `aggregateRating` for credibility and visibility in search results.
- Ensure all images have appropriate `alt` tags describing the content for better SEO.

### 3) Keyword Improvements

- Analyze current keyword usage and focus on long-tail keywords like:
  - "affordable custom garden sheds"
